'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/22814/', '', 'Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Abatacept, Upadacitinib, Apremilast, Inebilizumab, Cladribine, Belumosudil, Belimumab, More', 'Hydrochlorothiazide, Aliskiren, Ramipril, Valsartan, Rosuvastatin, Lisinopril, Perindopril, Niacin, Pravastatin, Acetylsalicylic acid, Ezetimibe, More', 1767369485);
